STATE EX REL. SUMMIT GASTROENTEROLOGY ASSOC., INC.
v.
MCCARTY 2018-0965 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 28, 2018

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur. O'DONNELL, J., dissents.
